{"image_id": "PHM_2018_page_70", "image_size": [1238, 1613], "ocr": [{"text": "PULTEGROUP, INC.", "bbox": [521.6, 27.8, 716.3, 50.9]}, {"text": "NOTES TO CONSOLIDATED FINANCIAL STATEMENTS (continued)", "bbox": [293.0, 52.8, 944.8, 75.9]}, {"text": "64", "bbox": [608.6, 1543.2, 629.4, 1566.2]}, {"text": "7. Stock compensation plans", "bbox": [85.5, 108.0, 336.7, 131.1]}, {"text": "We maintain a stock award plan for both employees and non-employee directors. The plan provides for the grant of a", "bbox": [141.7, 158.0, 1118.2, 181.1]}, {"text": "variety of equity awards, including options (generally non-qualified options), restricted shares, restricted share units (\"RSUs\"),", "bbox": [85.5, 183.1, 1147.3, 206.1]}, {"text": "and performance shares to key employees (as determined by the Compensation and Management Development Committee of", "bbox": [85.5, 208.1, 1138.2, 231.1]}, {"text": "the Board of Directors) for periods not to exceed ten years. Non-employee directors are awarded an annual distribution of", "bbox": [85.5, 233.1, 1105.5, 256.1]}, {"text": "common shares. Options granted to employees generally vest incrementally over four years and are generally exercisable for", "bbox": [85.5, 258.1, 1130.9, 281.1]}, {"text": "ten years from the vest date.  Shares issued upon the exercise of a stock option are from newly issued shares. RSUs represent", "bbox": [85.5, 283.1, 1132.5, 306.2]}, {"text": "the right to receive an equal number of common shares and are converted into common shares upon distribution. Restricted", "bbox": [85.5, 308.1, 1119.7, 331.2]}, {"text": "shares and RSUs generally cliff vest after three years. Both restricted share and RSU holders receive cash dividends during the", "bbox": [85.5, 333.1, 1147.2, 356.2]}, {"text": "vesting period. Performance shares vest upon attainment of the stated performance targets and minimum service requirements", "bbox": [85.5, 358.1, 1140.6, 381.2]}, {"text": "and are converted into common shares upon distribution. As of December 31, 2018, there were 24.4 million shares that", "bbox": [85.5, 383.1, 1083.0, 406.2]}, {"text": "remained available for grant under the plan. Our stock compensation expense for the three years ended December 31, 2018, is", "bbox": [85.5, 408.1, 1140.9, 431.2]}, {"text": "presented below ($000's omitted):", "bbox": [85.5, 433.1, 368.8, 456.2]}, {"text": "2018", "bbox": [698.2, 476.5, 739.9, 499.6]}, {"text": "2017", "bbox": [810.7, 476.5, 852.4, 499.6]}, {"text": "2016", "bbox": [923.3, 476.5, 965.0, 499.6]}, {"text": "Stock options", "bbox": [243.8, 507.8, 357.9, 530.9]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [673.2, 505.9, 683.6, 529.0]}, {"text": "—", "bbox": [743.3, 505.9, 764.2, 529.0]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [785.7, 505.9, 796.2, 529.0]}, {"text": "—", "bbox": [855.9, 505.9, 876.7, 529.0]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [898.3, 505.9, 908.7, 529.0]}, {"text": "—", "bbox": [968.4, 505.9, 989.3, 529.0]}, {"text": "Restricted shares (including RSUs and", "bbox": [243.8, 539.1, 565.7, 562.1]}, {"text": "performance shares)", "bbox": [243.8, 559.9, 413.5, 583.0]}, {"text": "20,145", "bbox": [706.8, 537.2, 764.2, 560.3]}, {"text": "24,207", "bbox": [819.4, 537.2, 876.7, 560.3]}, {"text": "18,626", "bbox": [931.9, 537.2, 989.3, 560.3]}, {"text": "Long-term incentive plans", "bbox": [243.8, 591.2, 463.9, 614.2]}, {"text": "8,145", "bbox": [717.3, 589.3, 764.2, 612.4]}, {"text": "9,476", "bbox": [829.8, 589.3, 876.7, 612.4]}, {"text": "3,602", "bbox": [942.4, 589.3, 989.3, 612.4]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [673.2, 622.4, 683.6, 645.5]}, {"text": "28,290", "bbox": [706.8, 622.4, 764.2, 645.5]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [785.7, 622.4, 796.2, 645.5]}, {"text": "33,683", "bbox": [819.4, 622.4, 876.7, 645.5]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [898.3, 622.4, 908.7, 645.5]}, {"text": "22,228", "bbox": [931.9, 622.4, 989.3, 645.5]}, {"text": "Stock options", "bbox": [85.5, 681.1, 197.2, 704.2]}, {"text": "A summary of stock option activity for the three years ended December 31, 2018, is presented b